  "title": "Draftman (Up to $3600 / 5 days)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Draftman (ID6050)<br />Location: Singapore based (depend on project)<br />Working Hours: Monday- Friday : 8:30am-5:30pm<br />Salary: $3000-$3600<br /><br />Roles & Responsibilities:<br />• Prepare detailed architectural and structural shop drawings using AutoCAD, ensuring compliance with project specifications.<br />• Support the project team by providing accurate and timely drawings for construction use.<br />• Coordinate with the Engineering Department and Project Team to resolve discrepancies in drawings.<br />• Develop drawings and specifications based on Client/Consultant requirements.<br />• Prepare as-built drawings for submission upon project completion.<br />• Assist with tender bids by producing floor plans and sectional drawings.<br />• Ensure all drawings are completed accurately and delivered on time.<br /><br />Job Requirement<br />• 2 years and above Structural / Architectural based</p>",
